The '''Warmaster's command grotto''' was a room grown for [[Warmaster]] [[Nas Choka]]. Located deep with the bowels of [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra's]] [[Shimrra's Citadel|Citadel]], the command grotto served as a war-room for the Warmaster, where he would consult his [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commanders]], [[Battle Tactician]]s, and high ranking [[Priest/Legends|Priests]] and [[Seer (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Seers]]. The room also featured a [[yorik coral]] niche which contained [[Blaze bug/Legends|blaze bugs]], that showed representations of enemy movements in far off systems.

